text: Carlo Bonfanti (7 July 1875 - 7 December 1933) was an Italian diver. He competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1933 deaths Category:Italian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Italy Category:Divers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milan
